<br>
9) Under *no* circumstances should guilds of the KGC engage in activity that could get them warned, banner or suspended and should avoid the use of foul or improper language.<br>
<br>
If it looks like those not recognizing the KGC rotation are going to engage a target before forces are ready. It is strongly encouraged to aggro and kite those targets which can be kited. <br>
