<br>
Shattering Steel was never a serious threat.  They were a joke and an annoyance.  But never a threat.  Its hard to call a guild a threat to the rotations that has a hard time breaking into PoF.<br>
<br>
Remember what happened to them?  After about 3 weeks where was SS?  Ummm...hmmmm...oh yeah...They were restricted to PoG.<br>
<br>
Why?<br>
<br>
Because everytime they went anywhere else the rest of the server pop'd in and wiped the zone for them and kept it wiped except for the 1 spawn they were able to claim.<br>
<br>
