<br>
Oh yes, and guilds like Fires of Heaven or Unity or Afterlife do contain half the server.  Every server with the exception of Karana has a guild that can field upwards of 500 people.  There is only 1 server where small guilds do more than simply serve as farm guilds for the uber guilds.  Only 1 server where you can see your epic mob even once a year.  The grass always seems greener next door, but I can assure you its painted.<br>
<br>
Frankly though, it all comes down to respect.  Do you respect others regardless of whether they are worthy of it or reciprocate it?<br>
<br>
Let me explain something quickly.<br>
<br>
No one remembers who founded The Haven or Ash or Grey Hawke or Valoran or Fama Volat or Blue Ribbon other than its members.  No one remembers The Combine other than a few old timers.  No one knows many of the guild leaders of most guilds.  Hell, most dont even know many of the guilds on the server.<br>
<br>
